{"tid":1807042,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"失去勇武，和理非猶如砧板上的肉 。","createTime":"2020-01-01T15:27:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-01T22:20:43.000Z","uid":239516,"like":24,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"17368e69349adf7b837b204c3cfa2db3bfee2341","tid":1807042,"uid":239516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:27:56.000Z","msg":"任人魚肉 為所欲為<br />\n失去了勇武的進場 失去了街頭抗爭<br />\n我們踏進了第7個月的抗爭了<br />\n依舊沒有任何一位執法犯法的黑警受到應有的法治制裁<br />\n當有立法會議員話有險可守 你會識笑識屌<br />\n你已經知道香港已經失去法治 <br />\n<br />\n以前你可以笑大陸既人治有幾可怕<br />\n依家即使先姦後殺 一樣都係公佈冇可疑<br />\n當黑警再沒有威脅 冇野可以阻撓依班有牌黑社會既為所欲為<br />\n即使幾多人受害 幾多年輕男女死去 被強姦 <br />\n<br />\n唔通我地既程度只係可以去到咁?<br />\n我唔係話我有方法解決 <br />\n而係想指出大家已經失去最初既警覺性 <br />\n對家已去到瘋狂既狀態 而你仲想用之前既方法去面對?"},{"pid":"7d146267b4599cc8cf1b51b69e9b2c22a573f16e","tid":1807042,"uid":239516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:30:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=j3rtsmGzjLU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dj3rtsmGzjLU&d=navV%2BA4%2FMRIetR8KyPOOAMeYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=8917642a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=j3rtsmGzjLU</a>"},{"pid":"619c082fb10da9c4204409ea40e26056725831f5","tid":1807042,"uid":313054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:31:15.000Z","msg":"咁點算"},{"pid":"687a31071917a14e9d6b94a5c3b6f437715fae22","tid":1807042,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:32:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b074427b7979362035d13c0b7342eeddd2ace8a2","tid":1807042,"uid":10881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:34:26.000Z","msg":"大家要keep 住努力<br />\n盡自己可以做到既方面做最多既野"},{"pid":"045b9448b4e893a52a01c7929a629f2d747f2064","tid":1807042,"uid":77905,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:34:59.000Z","msg":"仲有班撚屌捉鬼"},{"pid":"0637183e686c7bd28d7ee36b20384c7adb083b29","tid":1807042,"uid":74058,"like